  "names": [
    {
      "full_name": "All-Russian public-state movement of children and youth “Movement of the First”",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "“Movement of the First” is a state-led youth organisation in the Russian Federation, which was created in December 2022 at the initiative of President of the Russian Federation Vladimir Putin to provide educational activities, including of militarised nature, for children between the ages of 6 to 18, based on “traditional Russian spiritual and moral goals”. The children who are members of the movement have meetings with the soldiers who have fought in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine, send cards and letters of support to soldiers and also prepare equipment to be used on the battlefield, and learn how to handle drones. Additionally, the movement has organised war games for the children, which replicate and simulate battle situations.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}